JAVA Version 1.8
1. Create the JAVA Project
2. Create the lib folder 
3. Place the XML/Annotation Jar's in to /lib folder 
4. Add these JAR's in to Build path
5. Place the Hibernate Configuration i.e "hibernate.cfg.xml" in to */src folder 
6. Create the Package "com.simplilearn.hibernate" and placed the...
	6.1 POJO/ENTITY i.e Customer.java
	6.2 Customer.hbm.xml
	
	1-First Record
	2-Second Record
	
	
	
	select * from customers;
	
	Hibernate: 
	insert into customers (Name, Email, Phone, City, Bal, Cid) values (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	